            <title><![CDATA[【#热水泡脚确实能睡得更香# 】想要睡个好觉，是有讲究的[并不简单]张伯礼院士建议：1️⃣睡前放松；2️⃣热水泡脚；3️⃣睡前喝杯热牛奶；4️⃣睡眠时间不要过...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%83%AD%E6%B0%B4%E6%B3%A1%E8%84%9A%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9E%E8%83%BD%E7%9D%A1%E5%BE%97%E6%9B%B4%E9%A6%99%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%83%AD%E6%B0%B4%E6%B3%A1%E8%84%9A%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9E%E8%83%BD%E7%9D%A1%E5%BE%97%E6%9B%B4%E9%A6%99%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#热水泡脚确实能睡得更香#</span></a> 】想要睡个好觉，是有讲究的<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[并不简单]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_bingbujiandan-9955880b30.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>张伯礼院士建议：<br>1️⃣睡前放松；<br>2️⃣热水泡脚；<br>3️⃣睡前喝杯热牛奶；<br>4️⃣睡眠时间不要过早或过晚，起码保证睡6个~7个小时。<br><br>大家要以轻松的心态面对睡眠哦<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[抱一抱]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/co_a1hug-f3910d0e88.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>一起戳视频看看吧↓↓↓ <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4749452129534079" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1h0hg5nc0guj21hc0u00x3.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/L2twpMa8lx07UEpKoqm401041200iAby0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1704834847&amp;ssig=uksAjELzO1&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/GCkBZQaOlx07UEpJPjOM010412009FgR0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.28.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1704834847&amp;ssig=ggBF00Kk%2BC&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/qece5uo9lx07UEpK3WSk0104120060n60E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwC